Obituary for Jon Kevin Johnson
 Edit

Mr. Jon Kevin Johnson, age 59 of Griffin, passed away on Saturday, May 6, 2017 at Wellstar Spalding Hospital in Griffin. Mr. Johnson was born in Griffin, Georgia on December 3, 1957. He is preceded in death by his wife Lisa Johnson; grandchildren Aislyn and Claudia Isabelle; and his parents Jimmy Key Johnson, Sr. and Rebecca Frances Johnson.
Survivors include his son Russell and his wife Stephanie Johnson of Griffin; grandchildren Maddison and Jakeob; sister Angelyn and her husband Boyd Goss of Newnan ; brother Jimmy and his wife Ruth Johnson of Griffin and several nieces and nephews. 

Source : Conner-Westbury Funeral Home


